618
00:31:08,940 --> 00:31:10,100
If it gets out,

619
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:11,340
people will laugh at us

620
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:13,020
for being impolite.

621
00:31:13,020 --> 00:31:13,860
That's right.

622
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:16,020
Your Lordship,

623
00:31:16,020 --> 00:31:16,980
come in, please.

624
00:31:18,420 --> 00:31:19,940
Thank you, Madam Chu.

625
00:31:21,450 --> 00:31:22,820
But without Ms. Chu's permission,

626
00:31:23,940 --> 00:31:24,940
I wouldn't have it.

627
00:31:30,620 --> 00:31:31,460
Come in, please.

628
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:36,900
Make yourself at home.

629
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,460
Eat more.

630
00:31:39,100 --> 00:31:39,940
Thank you, Madam Chu.

631
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:41,500
Here. Have some more.

632
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:44,580
- It's enough.
- It's fine.

633
00:31:44,580 --> 00:31:46,100
- Really.
- Help yourself.

634
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:51,940
Yu,

635
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:53,580
I had our cook make this.

636
00:31:53,740 --> 00:31:54,580
Taste it.

637
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:56,220
Does it taste the same as before?

638
00:32:02,220 --> 00:32:03,060
It's delicious.

639
00:32:04,220 --> 00:32:05,060
Linyang,

640
00:32:05,940 --> 00:32:06,820
why do you only

641
00:32:06,820 --> 00:32:08,260
serve her food again?

642
00:32:11,900 --> 00:32:12,740
Here.

643
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:14,220
This is for you, Jin.

644
00:32:14,900 --> 00:32:15,740
Alright?

645
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:18,100
But I don't like fried fish.

646
00:32:19,380 --> 00:32:20,620
When Linyang serves you food,

647
00:32:20,900 --> 00:32:22,100
just say thank you.

648
00:32:22,460 --> 00:32:24,100
Don't be so obstinate.

649
00:32:24,260 --> 00:32:25,380
Or what will you do

650
00:32:25,580 --> 00:32:26,940
when you get married?

651
00:32:30,420 --> 00:32:31,260
Your Lordship,

652
00:32:32,220 --> 00:32:33,620
sorry for that.

653
00:32:33,860 --> 00:32:35,460
Please excuse her.

654
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:36,540
It's nothing.

655
00:32:36,900 --> 00:32:38,420
Don't worry, Madam Chu.

656
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:43,180
I knew

657
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:44,220
you would be

658
00:32:44,220 --> 00:32:45,420
a most polite man.

659
00:32:45,820 --> 00:32:46,940
Now your family

660
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:48,980
has restored its vitality.

661
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:50,740
Many matchmakers

662
00:32:50,740 --> 00:32:52,860
are scrambling
to arrange a marriage for you.

663
00:32:53,220 --> 00:32:54,300
I was wondering,

664
00:32:54,300 --> 00:32:55,420
have you decided
whom to marry?

665
00:33:00,780 --> 00:33:01,620
Not yet.

666
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:07,180
Your Lordship,

667
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:08,620
you're impressive.

668
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:11,100
At such a young age,
you've done much in war.

669
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:13,140
And you're from a noble family.

670
00:33:13,380 --> 00:33:15,380
You certainly have high standards.

671
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:17,380
It's too soon to think of that.

672
00:33:18,060 --> 00:33:18,900
Currently,

673
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:20,420
you're a leading general.

674
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:21,580
It's time you considered

675
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:23,340
your marriage thing.

676
00:33:25,220 --> 00:33:26,220
I have someone in mind

677
00:33:26,780 --> 00:33:28,940
who would be a good fit.

678
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:35,620
I wonder if you will

679
00:33:35,740 --> 00:33:36,740
think about it.

680
00:33:40,500 --> 00:33:42,620
You don't need
to get Chu Yu's consent.

681
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:44,780
Do you yourself want to?

682
00:34:02,380 --> 00:34:04,500
What do you think of our Chu Jin?

683
00:34:05,780 --> 00:34:06,620
- No.
- No.

684
00:34:10,260 --> 00:34:11,460
Why?

685
00:34:12,140 --> 00:34:13,380
You're both single.

686
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:14,580
Besides,

687
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:16,490
military families
have made repeated merits.

688
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,420
Now,

689
00:34:17,420 --> 00:34:18,500
His Majesty has permitted

690
00:34:18,780 --> 00:34:20,460
marriages between military families.

691
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:24,140
I can tell that you don't

692
00:34:24,340 --> 00:34:25,420
reject our family.

693
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:28,180
Chu Yu is a good woman.

694
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:31,140
Chu Jin is

695
00:34:31,460 --> 00:34:32,660
even better.

696
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:40,380
Mother has a point.

697
00:34:42,260 --> 00:34:43,100
However,

698
00:34:43,540 --> 00:34:44,780
the three of you said no.

699
00:34:45,300 --> 00:34:46,980
There should be reasons.

700
00:34:47,540 --> 00:34:48,620
Tell Mother the reasons.

701
00:34:50,660 --> 00:34:52,500
- Jin, you go first.
- I...

702
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:53,460
But I want Ms. Chu Yu

703
00:34:54,100 --> 00:34:54,940
to say it first.

704
00:35:01,420 --> 00:35:02,620
Anyone who lives

705
00:35:02,780 --> 00:35:03,700
in the Wei family

706
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:04,580
needs martial arts.

707
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:06,940
Jin has no martial arts at all.

708
00:35:08,380 --> 00:35:09,220
She can learn.

709
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:13,260
I can teach her.

710
00:35:20,340 --> 00:35:21,620
Why don't you tell me

711
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:24,060
what kind of woman

712
00:35:24,060 --> 00:35:24,900
would fit me?

713
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:30,060
A woman whom you like

714
00:35:30,820 --> 00:35:32,620
and who likes you back.

715
00:35:39,700 --> 00:35:40,540
Mother,

716
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:42,300
I'll never marry a man

717
00:35:42,300 --> 00:35:43,660
who goes to war.

718
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:45,220
This is my rule.

719
00:35:45,430 --> 00:35:46,300
- You...
- Yeah.

720
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:47,140
I agree.

721
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:48,500
Warriors may die in the war.

722
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:50,980
It's risky to marry me.

723
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:56,660
You guys talk.

724
00:35:57,380 --> 00:35:58,220
I have things to do.

725
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,300
I'll take my leave.

726
00:36:01,900 --> 00:36:02,740
Young Marquis,

727
00:36:05,660 --> 00:36:06,620
let's play chess.

728
00:36:07,180 --> 00:36:08,020
Shall we?

729
00:36:13,410 --> 00:36:14,260
Let's go.

730
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:15,220
Why are you taking me

731
00:36:15,220 --> 00:36:16,060
to Chu Mansion?

732
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:17,420
Jin doesn't want to see me.

733
00:36:18,620 --> 00:36:19,500
Didn't you say

734
00:36:19,780 --> 00:36:20,900
Young Marquis Wei

735
00:36:20,900 --> 00:36:21,860
took Mr. Lu's advice

736
00:36:21,860 --> 00:36:23,060
and delivered betrothal gifts?

737
00:36:23,150 --> 00:36:24,020
Don't you want

738
00:36:24,020 --> 00:36:24,860
to take a look?

739
00:36:26,020 --> 00:36:26,860
Besides,

740
00:36:27,220 --> 00:36:28,580
since when have you been so timid?

741
00:36:33,220 --> 00:36:34,500
Ms. Chu Jin doesn't come to you.

742
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:35,900
But you can go see her.

743
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,260
Right.

744
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:42,940
You're right.

745
00:36:43,300 --> 00:36:44,140
Let's go.

746
00:36:46,780 --> 00:36:47,740
Catch up.

747
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:51,420
You little fool.

748
00:36:51,860 --> 00:36:53,700
Young Marquis Wei is perfect.

749
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:55,060
Even your brother helps you

750
00:36:55,060 --> 00:36:56,220
to find out his thoughts.

751
00:36:56,420 --> 00:36:57,900
You must seize the opportunity.

752
00:36:58,420 --> 00:36:59,300
Oh, Mother.

753
00:37:00,490 --> 00:37:01,920
My heart belongs to someone else.

754
00:37:03,500 --> 00:37:04,780
I just haven't made up my mind.

755
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:08,350
Don't make a mismatch.

756
00:37:08,700 --> 00:37:09,940
I'm doing this for your good.

757
00:37:09,940 --> 00:37:11,060
You silly girl.

758
00:37:15,740 --> 00:37:17,140
So many dishes aren't finished.

759
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:51,620
Do you think this game

760
00:37:52,860 --> 00:37:53,700
can be won?

761
00:37:55,300 --> 00:37:56,500
It's not the end yet.

762
00:37:58,140 --> 00:37:58,980
No one can predict.

763
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:02,780
You're playing

764
00:38:03,180 --> 00:38:04,420
in quite an unusual way.

765
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:05,940
Special, indeed.

766
00:38:06,980 --> 00:38:07,820
Before, I didn't like

767
00:38:07,820 --> 00:38:08,660
to play like this.

768
00:38:10,900 --> 00:38:11,780
In that case,

769
00:38:12,340 --> 00:38:13,260
you're behaving

770
00:38:14,020 --> 00:38:15,460
quite like Yu.

771
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:23,490
There's nothing wrong
with being unusual.

772
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:25,540
Conforming isn't wrong, either.

773
00:38:26,340 --> 00:38:27,900
But when making a decision,

774
00:38:28,700 --> 00:38:29,580
one should ask himself

775
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:31,340
what he really wants.

776
00:38:32,260 --> 00:38:33,620
Sounds like you have

777
00:38:33,620 --> 00:38:34,700
thought very clearly.

778
00:38:37,740 --> 00:38:38,580
It won't be

779
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:42,100
an easy road.

780
00:38:47,340 --> 00:38:48,340
But if I do nothing,

781
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:51,140
I will regret it.

782
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:53,580
