783
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:55,460
But human life

784
00:38:57,300 --> 00:38:58,780
is always limited.

785
00:39:05,220 --> 00:39:06,060
Young Marquis,

786
00:39:07,060 --> 00:39:08,260
I have to remind you.

787
00:39:09,180 --> 00:39:10,380
You're accustomed to battles.

788
00:39:11,340 --> 00:39:12,300
But it doesn't mean

789
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,140
you can do

790
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:14,580
something else without scruple

791
00:39:14,580 --> 00:39:15,420
just like that.

792
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:17,500
I know you're impatient.

793
00:39:18,140 --> 00:39:19,020
But you have to wait

794
00:39:19,460 --> 00:39:21,260
and see if the other person has decided

795
00:39:21,860 --> 00:39:22,980
and whether she wants

796
00:39:24,660 --> 00:39:26,260
to fight a way out with you.

797
00:39:29,340 --> 00:39:30,220
By then,

798
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:33,940
will you help me

799
00:39:34,860 --> 00:39:35,980
remove the obstacles?

800
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:39,380
Or will you stand in my way?

801
00:39:41,140 --> 00:39:42,260
Yu is my sister

802
00:39:43,020 --> 00:39:44,500
and the pearl of this family.

803
00:39:45,740 --> 00:39:46,580
What I choose

804
00:39:47,540 --> 00:39:48,380
doesn't matter.

805
00:40:32,060 --> 00:40:35,510
♪If not for dreams by windswept flight♪

806
00:40:36,210 --> 00:40:39,360
